        <Parent_String>Colonial North American [300107812], Colonial American (pan-American style) [300018032], The Americas [300016617], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
